This paper is about a deep convolutional neural network for multi-modal image restoration and fusion. The paper proposes a novel network architecture that draws inspiration from a new proposed multi-modal convolutional sparse coding (MCSC) model. The paper focuses on computer vision and machine learning, which are subfields of computer science. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
